          <title>North Carolina football player Tylee Craft dies from rare lung cancer at 23</title>
          <description><![CDATA[North Carolina football player Tylee Craft died Saturday morning from a rare form of lung cancer, coach Mack Brown said. “This young man fought so hard for his two and a half years,” Brown said. “The doctors told us he outlived what he should’ve.]]></description>
